### What was done
- **Verified the owner's `GROQ_API_KEY`** without printing it: present/well-formed (gsk_, 56 chars), `.env` gitignored + untracked, HTTP 200, `openai/gpt-oss-120b` available + non-deprecated (RULES §6).
